{
  a: 〈0;#A〉
  a: {
    c: 1
  }
  #A: {}
}
-- out/todo.txt --
v2 reports additional error positions (in.cue:1:4 and in.cue:3:5) for the "field
not allowed" error on a.c. v3 only reports the direct field definition position
(in.cue:2:4).
